---
Source:
  - Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
    Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
    Translator: Red Pine
    ISBN: 1556591403
    Page: 253
By: Han Shan
---
On Cold Mountain Road
no one arrives
those who walk it
are called ten names
cicadas sing
crows don't screech
yellow leaves fall
white clouds sweep
rocks are huge
woods are deep
I live here alone
I'm called the Guide
look around
what are my signs
